outputs.output_descr: Improved capacity of the National Parliament to enable the efficient and effective performance of oversight, accountability, legislative and representative functions and roles including improved capacity for equitable representation and participatory democracy through civic and human rights education.  It  intermediate outcome is: MPs better equipped to undertaking their parliamentary functions including law making, representation including constituency relations at both local and national level and oversight of the executive.
